oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Cedarcrest Jamboree - 1949-04-09 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: WSM's Cedarcrest Jamboree, originally broadcast 1949-04-09, part 2. Previous cataloging notes the record date as 1949-04-06, as stated on a label, now missing. Hosted by Louie Buck and Cowboy Copas, with Lazy Jim Day, Little Jimmy Dickens, and Red Herron. Sponsored by Cedarcrest shoes.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Cowboy Copas; Lazy Jim Day; Little Jimmy Dickens
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: The Old Rugged Cross (Cowboy Copas) -- Louie Buck introduces Lazy Jim Day -- Lazy Jim Day talks -- Singing News (Lazy Jim Day) -- Louie Buck introduces Little Jimmy Dickens -- I'm Fading Fast With The Time (Little Jimmy Dickens) -- Louie Buck and Cowboy Copas talk about the Cedarcrest contest -- Breeze (Cowboy Copas) -- [Unidentified fiddle tune] (Red Herron fiddle, Lazy Jim Day calls) -- Closing statement (Cowboy Copas) -- Cedarcrest shoes commercial (Louie Buck) -- Theme (Filipino Baby (Cowboy Copas)) -- Closing statement (Louie Buck)
